## Config change

Add to `Config$Server`:

```java
public final ModConfigSpec.DoubleValue anotherPlayerBackpackOpenMaxDistance;
// ...
anotherPlayerBackpackOpenMaxDistance = builder
    .comment("Maximum distance (blocks) at which a player can open another player's backpack.")
    .defineInRange("anotherPlayerBackpackOpenMaxDistance", 6.0D, 0.0D, 64.0D);
```

## Moderation aid (optional)

Log the opener's name + target's name + backpack identifier to the server log when an open succeeds. This makes abuse auditable after the fact without disrupting legitimate use.
